<br>
If yer Monk or SK is good .. he/she can FD to where Ptassa is (tracking from the safewall helps determine which spot he spawned) to see if he's holding the staff.  If he has it, start clearing to get a clean pull on him.<br>
<br>
Disclaimer:  This tactic kind of requires belonging to a capable guild who's willing to help you.  Unfortunately, getting a staff by going up to Hate on a pickup raid is very tough .. the odds are against you.<br>
